      • readSet

        public static java.util.Set<Trace<AtomicEvent>> readSet(java.util.Scanner scanner)
        Reads a set of traces from a text input source. The source must be made of text structured as follows:
        • Each trace is on one line
        • Events are separated by commas
        • Any leading or trailing whitespace is trimmed for each event
        • Empty lines, and lines beginning by "#" are ignored
        Obviously, this method of reading traces only works for reasonably small, static sets.
        Parameters:
        scanner - A scanner open on the source to read
        Returns:
        The set of traces read from the scanner
